{"questionId":"3377547","questionHtml":"<p>Find an exact expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>l</mi></math> in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>equating a volume of a half cylinder (or cylinder) to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>l</mi></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Do not accept decimal approximation of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></math> for the <em><strong>A1</strong></em> given the demand of question.</p>\n<p>Condone the use of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>h</mi></math> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>l</mi></math> for the <em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3377547","referenceCode":"23M.2.SL.TZ1.5a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find an exact expression for l in terms of r and π.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","SL 3.1—3d space, volume, angles, midpoints"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}